{"tid":581691,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(估職業)錢幣店失5張古董鈔 警放蛇拘＿＿＿","createTime":"2018-03-05T14:18:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-05T14:21:01.000Z","uid":5253,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2d712b7e9069c40049d2d23161e2720c22713141","tid":581691,"uid":5253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T14:18:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180305/large/1520258966_4db1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180305%2Flarge%2F1520258966_4db1.jpg&h=96147324&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n旺角砵蘭街163-173號好旺角購物中心一家錢幣店，於上月26日下午疑被人偷去5張面值港幣50元的古董鈔票，53歲姓吳負責人其後發現有人在網上兜售該5張鈔票，遂於上周五向警方報案。<br />\n<br />\n警方接報後派員假扮買家表示對這些鈔票有興趣，並相約賣家在旺角區見面，結果對方應約現身；其間警員拘捕涉案兩名分別35歲姓鍾和58歲姓黃的男子，經調查後，更發現鍾為休班警務人員。<br />\n兩人涉嫌盜竊，已獲准保釋候查，須於4月中旬向警方報到。案件交由旺角警區刑事調查隊跟進。警方強調，如任何人員干犯違法行為，警隊定必嚴正處理。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家有冇估中<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f9e2b7ef0d6db0e0918b7aa5426bffc1a8f0470","tid":581691,"uid":40628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T14:18:53.000Z","msg":"大熱勝出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be96155b87155c483b005ada6d9754b28df48131","tid":581691,"uid":45788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T14:21:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Goal!!</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}